sible for presenting point-based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap "},{"code":"UIImage","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationImage"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","type":"topic"}}}